{"tid":2477964,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"教育局將向全港中小學派發教材《我的家在中國》　教材作古仔","createTime":"2021-04-06T16:42:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-06T17:31:17.000Z","uid":261647,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"14ec96e3cedea217c77dca89c0019467c17fe6bd","tid":2477964,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T16:42:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210402/PM2ISNTWI5FZNH6EG4VR2LJAGQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210402%2FPM2ISNTWI5FZNH6EG4VR2LJAGQ%2F&d=PGvktPFvO8uhCwWWOTiXtTvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=2042bf90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210402%2FPM2ISNTWI5FZNH6EG4VR2LJAGQ%2F&h=af351a8e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210402/PM2ISNTWI5FZNH6EG4VR2LJAGQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n教育局將向全港中小學派發內地國情教育書《我的家在中國》最新繁體版，列為輔助教材及局方中史常識問答比賽參考讀物。<br />\n<br />\n歷史學者：如教學生2+2=5<br />\n<br />\n《我的家在中國》其中一冊《祖國生日快樂──國慶節》中提到一個故事，指1990年北京中學生梁帆應聯合國兒童基金會邀請，參加在荷蘭舉行的「世界兒童為未來」活動，當她看到50多國的國旗掛在賓館前獨缺中國，便向活動方人員說「一定要升起中國的國旗，因為我來自中國！」然後在她一再要求下，「幾經周折，鮮艷的五星紅旗終於高高飄揚在諾維克上空」。<br />\n<br />\n歷史學者楊穎宇表示，經考證該故事最早官方版本出自2010年的《中國教育報》，但地點是廣場而非賓館前，網上有該故事不同版本，有名字叫于瑩的、其身份是小學生的、年份是1994年等，搜尋「荷蘭諾維克」結果亦全與這「故事」有關。他查考地圖和《外國地名譯名手冊》，找不到荷蘭有「諾維克」此地名；找來1990年聯合國兒童基金會報告，巨細無遺羅列當年活動，但也找不到活動曾在「荷蘭諾維克」舉辦。<br />\n<br />\n楊質疑該套書部份選材不嚴謹，假故事的出現不知有心還是無意，但若選材真確性成疑，當然不適合用來做教材，否則將假故事當真知識來教，「等於教學生2+2=5」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSilver Silk:<br />\n真有特色：無中生有！自己幻想的故事！<br />\n<br />\nSian Lo Lung:<br />\n「家在中國」就己經係作故仔。對於香港同香港人，中共係不折不扣外部勢力，根本一堆中國嘢唔係香港嘢，我地喺香港根本就唔同喺中國，咁嘅教材只係違反現實。"},{"pid":"8bd6bd207cdc0f2fb1b362dbc09bd77db8d6ecfc","tid":2477964,"uid":142358,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T16:43:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPA8nnuGiWe467UCyPrvFxeQm8QL14dHqUxkyuidaV817?filename=25qLMXA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F25qLMXA.gif&h=48c6000b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4251a3eaa71b5655aa142c2888d9e84c7eecd46e","tid":2477964,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T16:45:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ec27f86136f5a9973e15f5ccaf0b06ce3baff600","tid":2477964,"uid":74532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bd6bd207cdc0f2fb1b362dbc09bd77db8d6ecfc","tid":2477964,"uid":142358,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T16:43:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/25qLMXA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F25qLMXA.gif&h=48c6000b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T16:46:39.000Z","msg":"Block"},{"pid":"5418d25678dda2cff3e97857ea4c66da3eccb24e","tid":2477964,"uid":282637,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T16:46:40.000Z","msg":"Silver Silk:<br />\n真有特色：無中生有！自己幻想的故事！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c5aba7f0fb8bc83e25a2a130857b31a1aa74b5d","tid":2477964,"uid":23392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T16:48:24.000Z","msg":"已封鎖會員 - 刃刃卒(茶杯茶杯)"},{"pid":"129889d8e8b3045b8d1ab1790167b04f87d4ec0d","tid":2477964,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T16:49:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5600ed857d442689dec120f5d25fc6be8f98f449","tid":2477964,"uid":127067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T17:18:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45aa5f41340d6747c490d41b63a1844d28f3fc24","tid":2477964,"uid":264771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T17:21:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b48cd8f49a6679ac4ee736010fdcbe49c9a08401","tid":2477964,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T17:28:38.000Z","msg":"已封鎖會員 刃刃卒(茶杯茶杯)"},{"pid":"4b9f1cd2c045212fcba18dd80f41b66f69720eb6","tid":2477964,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T17:30:35.000Z","msg":"將愛國教條化庸俗化<br />\n漢奸教育局又搞低級紅"},{"pid":"93af64beb55fa5943f0ce04dd5335e92f85833e2","tid":2477964,"uid":69841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T17:31:17.000Z","msg":"準備以後啲歷史教科書都係作<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/miracle_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}